metadata.name: Planet Namara
metadata.description:
That's from that time I went to see the wonderous "Floating Bubble Mountains" on Planet Namara. 

A fascinating optical illusion caused by the blending of lights from the two suns near the planet.

Stunning views! 

Also got the chance to go on a hike in the beautiful "Purple Mountains".
